Description

Bakery - Cafe - Takeaway - Wholesale and retail bakery specialising in pretzels, pies, sourdoughs and European breads.   • Features: Unique products.Well known within the hotel industry for quality of products. Only 2 owners in 20 years. Very low rent.

  • Employees: 1 working owner 5 bakers plus delivery drivers.
  • Sale Reason: Family commitments and other ventures.
  • Comments: Equipment includes walk- in coolroom, freezers, 10 deck oven, 3 mixers, 1 Hobart mixer, 2 group coffee machine, 1 new cake display fridge and 1 cake carousel. Van not included in price.
    A new 2 group coffee machine is fully owned and purchased in July 2020 for $15,000.
